caption:
The photograph showcases a serene rural setting featuring two houses nestled in a verdant landscape. The house in the foreground is a classic white two-story building with green shutters. It has a noticeably traditional architectural style, including a covered front porch partially visible to the viewer. In the adjacent yard, there are fence-enclosed areas that appear to be used for small-scale farming or livestock.

The background features a second house, which sits at a higher elevation on the hillside. This house has a more modern design with yellow siding and large windows, and it is surrounded by a wrap-around deck. There's a notable contrast in the architectural styles and color schemes of the two houses, reflecting a blend of old and new.

The surroundings include a lush wooded area that envelops the scene, intensifying the feeling of a secluded rural retreat. The landscape is also marked by rolled hay or fencing materials scattered near the houses, enhancing the agricultural feel. Additionally, there is a car parked beside the house in the background, suggesting recent habitation or activity. The overall atmosphere conveyed by the image is peaceful and quaint, typical of a countryside environment.
title: View of the homes of jerri fisher, who lives in the countryside near poulsbo.  The white house is his "first generation" home and the one beyond it his "second generation" home.  These houses are in an area which will be affected by population growth when the navy's proposed trident submarine base is built nearby
